The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Most goals in opening match

 Fridays opening match between 

 Germany and Costa Rica saw six goals being scored. Following 

 is the list of the maximum number of goals scored in a World 

 Cup opener

 10 ? France (7) bt Paraguay (3) in Norrk?ping, 

 Sweden (June 8, 1958)

 8 ? Italy (7) bt USA (1) in Rome (May 27, 1934)

 7 ? Germany (5) bt Belgium (2) in Florence (May 

 27, 1934)

 6 ? Hungary (4) bt Egypt (2) in Naples (May 27, 

 1934)

 6 ? Germany (4) bt Costa Rica (2) in Munich (June 

 6, 2006) 

 5 ? France (4) bt Mexico (1) in Montevideo (July 

 13, 1930) 

 Note: In 1934 and 1958, 

 eight first round matches began simultaneously

